<module>
    <h>beag</h>
    <p><g>beag</g>
        <en>small, little</en> is a <a href="?xx=adjectives/simple_adjectives">simple
        adjective</a>.</p>

    <section>
        <h>uses</h>
        <section id="uses-predicate">
            <h>predicate</h>
            <p><g>beag</g> can be used as the predicate of the verb <a href="?gd=bi"
                ><g>bi</g></a>.</p>
            <p>Examples with a human subject – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Màiri <m>beag</m>.</gd>
                        <tr>Mary is small.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 6</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <p>Examples with an animal subject – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha an cat <m>beag</m>.</gd>
                        <tr>The cat is small.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 6</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <p>Examples with more than one predicate – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Màiri <m>beag bàn</m>.</gd>
                        <tr>Mary is small and fair-haired.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 8</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
        <section id="uses-mod">
            <h>modifier</h>
            <p><g>beag</g> can be used to modify a <a href="?xx=nouns/proper_nouns">proper
                noun</a>.</p>
            <p>Some examples – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha <m>Màiri bheag</m> bàn.</gd>
                        <tr>Little Mary is fair-haired.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 9</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>

    </section>

